Hearing Aid is a perfect tool for sound amplification. It uses the microphone of the mobile phone to monitor on-site, collect the sound, increase the volume and eliminate the noise through the application, and then play it through the earphones. Use this hearing aid application to achieve sound reception and amplification, Noise reduction, to achieve mobile phone hearing aid effects.

SUPPORT BACKGROUND MODE
- This app could perfectly supports real-time sound amplification when the iPhone is in lock screen and background mode.

SCENARIOS OF USING
- Self-help hearing test: Ear age test, you can pay attention to your ears and hearing health regularly like using an eye chart, and prevent yourself, your family, and friends from hearing damage caused by long-term exposure to noise.
- Daily Ear Care Exercises: 6 steps of daily ear exercises, 5 minutes a day to protect the ear, prevent and delay hearing loss.
- Hearing aids for the hearing impaired: You can use your mobile phone as a hearing aid in daily conversations, watching TV, meetings, etc.
- Intelligent noise reduction: Automatically reduce noise through artificial intelligence technology, support custom use scenarios, and make conversations clearer and easier to understand.

MAIN FEATURES
-Detect the environmental noise and preset volume amplification schemes for different scenes such as outdoor, home, conference, office, movie theater, etc.;
-Automatically adjust the hearing aid compensation according to your hearing situation, and adjust the volume for the left and right ears respectively to achieve an enhanced effect;
-Suitable for daily face-to-face conversations, watching TV, meetings, classrooms, interviews, and other different scenarios;
-It can reduce the noise and eliminate the environmental noise while increasing the volume to ensure a balanced sound recognition quality;
-The phone microphone and headset microphone can be switched to adapt to different usage scenarios;
-With the tuner function, you can control and adjust the volume and fine-tune the sound amplification effect;
-Need to be used with earphones, it is recommended to use original earphones that match the mobile phone brand;
-Effectively reduce influencing factors such as delay and echo, making the dialogue clearer and easier to hear;
-Ear age test, you can complete the auditory self-examination within 2 minutes, saving the time and money of visiting an audiologist;
-An alternative hearing aid program for hearing impaired people such as deafness and tinnitus, used when the hearing aid is out of power and forgot to wear the hearing aid.

DISCLAIMER
-Hearing aid application software is a hearing health aid software, not a hearing medical device.
-The hearing test results are only for reference and configuration of this application, and cannot replace the ear doctor's diagnosis.

